      "Replaced 643 implausible values (0 < income < 100)\n",
      "Imputed 30,374 missing values with log-median: 8.5973\n",
      "\n",
      "MonthlyIncome after log transformation:\n",
      "  Min: 0.0000  (= log(1+0) for zero income)\n",
